Who's Hitotose?

5
00:00:08,190 --> 00:00:10,980
- Aren't you talking about Hitotose?
- Aren't you talking about Murai?

6
00:00:10,980 --> 00:00:13,250
<i>My boss has discovered I'm a hopeless otaku,</i>

7
00:00:13,250 --> 00:00:17,160
<i>no thanks to that nightmarish evening.</i>

8
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:21,250
<i>Meanwhile, Murai-kun suspects I have something going on with Boss,</i>

9
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:23,550
<i>and has put some respectable distance with me.</i>

10
00:00:23,550 --> 00:00:29,080
<i>However, one event was about to change everything.</i>

11
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:34,400
You all know Takebe High's annual Winter Camping Trip with the Vice-Principal.

12
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:37,980
For those interested, I shall be chaperoning this year's trip.

13
00:00:37,980 --> 00:00:42,560
This is a great opportunity to suck up to your teachers.

14
00:00:45,700 --> 00:00:48,750
Looks like Mr. Vice Principal was next in line for a cold,

15
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:51,310
and three days before camp too.
<i>[Steel yourself! 3 Days Until the Camping Trip]</i>

16
00:00:51,310 --> 00:00:54,880
You'll be the only chaperone, okay?

17
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,610
I'm anything but okay.

18
00:00:56,610 --> 00:00:57,810
Thought so.

19
00:00:57,810 --> 00:00:58,850
<i>[Day of the Trip]</i>

20
00:00:58,850 --> 00:01:02,800
And so, I'm joining as an emergency chaperone.

21
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,770
Thank you, Sir.

22
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,900
Did you hear? Hirai's got a fever of forty degrees.

23
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:09,200
Also sir, it's raining.

24
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:11,690
That's what it means to camp.

25
00:01:11,690 --> 00:01:15,940
Prepare yourselves for a day of Sensei  Tanaka planned fun.

26
00:01:15,940 --> 00:01:19,220
Please don't raise their expectations.

27
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:25,850
You two...

28
00:01:25,850 --> 00:01:28,260
sure get along.

29
